 class=\"vlist-s\">​</span></span><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:0.2861em;\"><span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span> 表示用户 <span v-pre class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>u</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">u</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.4306em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">u</span></span></span></span> 对物品 <span v-pre class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>i</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">i</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.6595em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">i</span></span></span></span> 的评分，未评分的地方为空值。</p>\n<h2 id=\"⚔️-协同过滤的两大门派\" tabindex=\"-1\"><a class=\"header-anchor\" href=\"#⚔️-协同过滤的两大门派\"><span>⚔️ 协同过滤的两大门派</span></a></h2>\n<h3 id=\"基于用户的协同过滤-user-based-cf\" tabindex=\"-1\"><a class=\"header-anchor\" href=\"#基于用户的协同过滤-user-based-cf\"><span>基于用户的协同过滤 (User-based CF)</span></a></h3>\n<div class=\"hint-container info\">\n<p class=\"hint-container-title\">用户视角</p>\n<p>&quot;告诉我你的朋友是谁，我就知道你是什么样的人&quot;</p>\n</div>\n<p><strong>核心思想</strong>：找到与目标用户兴趣相似的用户群体，推荐这些相似用户喜欢但目标用户未接触过的物品。</p>\n<p><strong>算法步骤</strong>：</p>\n<ol>\n<li>计算用户之间的相似度</li>\n<li>找到最相似的K个用户（邻居）</li>\n<li>基于邻居的偏好预测目标用户的偏好</li>\n<li>推荐评分最高的物品</li>\n</ol>\n<p><strong>用户相似度计算</strong>：</p>\n<p>皮尔逊相关系数：</p>\n<p v-pre class='katex-block'><span class=\"katex-display\"><span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" display=\"block\"><semantics><mrow><mi>s</mi><mi>i</mi><mi>m</mi><mo stretchy=\"false\">(</mo><mi>u</mi><mo separator=\"true\">,</mo><mi>v</mi><mo stretchy=\"false\">)</mo><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><munder><mo>∑</mo><mrow><mi>i</mi><mo>∈</mo><msub><mi>I</mi><mrow><mi>u</mi><mi>v</mi></mrow></msub></mrow></munder><mo stretchy=\"false\">(</mo><msub><mi>r</mi><mrow><mi>u</mi><mo separator=\"true\">,</mo><mi>i</mi></mrow></msub><mo>−</mo><mover accent=\"true\"><msub><mi>r</mi><mi>u</mi></msub><mo>ˉ</mo></mover><mo stretchy=\"false\">)</mo><mo stretchy=\"false\">(</mo><msub><mi>r</mi><mrow><mi>v</mi><mo separator=\"true\">,</mo><mi>i</mi></mrow></msub><mo>−</mo><mover accent=\"true\"><msub><mi>r</mi><mi>v</mi></msub><mo>ˉ</mo></mover><mo stretchy=\"false\">)</mo></mrow><mrow><msqrt><mrow><munder><mo>∑</mo><mrow><mi>i</mi><mo>∈</mo><msub><mi>I</mi><mrow><mi>u</mi><mi>v</mi></mrow></msub></mrow></munder><mo stretchy=\"false\">(</mo><msub><mi>r</mi><mrow><mi>u</mi><mo separator=\"true\">,</mo><mi>i</mi></mrow></msub><mo>−</mo><mover accent=\"true\"><msub><mi>r</mi><mi>u</mi></msub><mo>ˉ</mo></mover><msup><mo stretchy=\"false\">)</mo><mn>2</mn></msup></mrow></msqrt><msqrt><mrow><munder><mo>∑</mo><mrow><mi>i</mi><mo>∈</mo><msub><mi>I</mi><mrow><mi>u</mi><mi>v</mi></mrow></msub></mrow></munder><mo stretchy=\"false\">(</mo><msub><mi>r</mi><mrow><mi>v</mi><mo separator=\"true\">,</mo><mi>i</mi></mrow></msub><mo>−</mo><mover accent=\"true\"><msub><mi>r</mi><mi>v</mi></msub><mo>ˉ</mo></mover><msup><mo stretchy=\"false\">)</mo><mn>2</mn></msup></mrow></msqrt></mrow></mfrac></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">sim(u,v) = \\frac{\\sum_{i \\in I_{uv}}(r_{u,i} - \\bar{r_u})(r_{v,i} - \\bar{r_v})}{\\sqrt{\\sum_{i \\in I_{uv}}(r_{u,i} - \\bar{r_u})^2} \\sqrt{\\sum_{i \\in I_{uv}}(r_{v,i} - \\bar{r_v})^2}}\n</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">s</span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">im</span><span class=\"mopen\">(</span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">u</span><span class=\"mpunct\">,</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.1667em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.03588em;\">v</span><span class=\"mclose\">)</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span><span class=\"mrel\">=</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:3.2698em;vertical-align:-1.73em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mopen nulldelimiter\"></span><span class=\"mfrac\"><span class=\"vlist-t vlist-t2\"><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:1.5398em;\"><span style=\"top:-2.11em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:3.1601em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mord sqrt\"><span class=\"vlist-t vlist-t2\"><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:1.1601em;\"><span class=\"svg-align\" style=\"top:-3.8em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:3.8em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\" style=\"padding-left:1em;\"><span class=\"mop\"><span class=\"mop op-symbol small-op\" style=\"position:relative;top:0em;\">∑</span><span class=\"msupsub\"><span class=\"vlist-t vlist-t2\"><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:0.1786em;\"><span style=\"top:-2.4003em;margin-left:0em;margin-right:0.05em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:2.7em;\"></span><span class=\"sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight\"><span class=\"mord mtight\"><span class=\"mord mathnormal mtight\">i</span><span class=\"mrel mtight\">∈</span><span class=\"mord mtight\"><span class=\"mord mathnormal mtight\" style=\"margin-right:0.07847em;\">I</span><span class=\"msupsub\"><span class=\"vlist-t vlist-t2\"><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:0.1645em;\"><span style=\"top:-2.357em;margin-left:-0.0785em;margin-right:0.0714em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:2.5em;\"></span><span class=\"sizing reset-size3 size1 mtight\"><