span></span></span><span class=\"mclose nulldelimiter\"></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\n<h3 id=\"基于物品的协同过滤-item-based-cf\" tabindex=\"-1\"><a class=\"header-anchor\" href=\"#基于物品的协同过滤-item-based-cf\"><span>基于物品的协同过滤 (Item-based CF)</span></a></h3>\n<div class=\"hint-container info\">\n<p class=\"hint-container-title\">物品视角</p>\n<p>&quot;物以类聚：相似的物品会被相似的用户群体喜欢&quot;</p>\n</div>\n<p><strong>核心思想</strong>：计算物品之间的相似度，推荐与用户历史偏好物品相似的物品。</p>\n<p><strong>物品相似度计算</strong>：</p>\n<p>余弦相似度：</p>\n<p v-pre class='katex-block'><span class=\"katex-display\"><span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" display=\"block\"><semantics><mrow><mi>s</mi><mi>i</mi><mi>m</mi><mo stretchy=\"false\">(</mo><mi>i</mi><mo separator=\"true\">,</mo><mi>j</mi><mo stretchy=\"false\">)</mo><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><munder><mo>∑</mo><mrow><mi>u</mi><mo>∈</mo><msub><mi>U</mi><mrow><mi>i</mi><mi>j</mi></mrow></msub></mrow></munder><msub><mi>r</mi><mrow><mi>u</mi><mo separator=\"true\">,</mo><mi>i</mi></mrow></msub><mo>⋅</mo><msub><mi>r</mi><mrow><mi>u</mi><mo separator=\"true\">,</mo><mi>j</mi></mrow></msub></mrow><mrow><msqrt><mrow><munder><mo>∑</mo><mrow><mi>u</mi><mo>∈</mo><msub><mi>U</mi><mrow><mi>i</mi><mi>j</mi></mrow></msub></mrow></munder><msubsup><mi>r</mi><mrow><mi>u</mi><mo separator=\"true\">,</mo><mi>i</mi></mrow><mn>2</mn></msubsup></mrow></msqrt><msqrt><mrow><munder><mo>∑</mo><mrow><mi>u</mi><mo>∈</mo><msub><mi>U</mi><mrow><mi>i</mi><mi>j</mi></mrow></msub></mrow></munder><msubsup><mi>r</mi><mrow><mi>u</mi><mo separator=\"true\">,</mo><mi>j</mi></mrow><mn>2</mn></msubsup></mrow></msqrt></mrow></mfrac></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">sim(i,j) = \\frac{\\sum_{u \\in U_{ij}} r_{u,i} \\cdot r_{u,j}}{\\sqrt{\\sum_{u \\in U_{ij}} r_{u,i}^2} \\sqrt{\\sum_{u \\in U_{ij}} r_{u,j}^2}}\n</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">s</span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">im</span><span class=\"mopen\">(</span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">i</span><span class=\"mpunct\">,</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.1667em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.05724em;\">j</span><span class=\"mclose\">)</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span><span class=\"mrel\">=</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:3.367em;vertical-align:-1.73em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mopen nulldelimiter\"></span><span class=\"mfrac\"><span class=\"vlist-t vlist-t2\"><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:1.637em;\"><span style=\"top:-2.11em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:3.1344em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mord sqrt\"><span class=\"vlist-t vlist-t2\"><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:1.1344em;\"><span class=\"svg-align\" style=\"top:-3.8em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:3.8em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\" style=\"padding-left:1em;\"><span class=\"mop\"><span class=\"mop op-symbol small-op\" style=\"position:relative;top:0em;\">∑</span><span class=\"msupsub\"><span class=\"vlist-t vlist-t2\"><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:0.1786em;\"><span style=\"top:-2.4003em;margin-left:0em;margin-right:0.05em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:2.7em;\"></span><span class=\"sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight\"><span class=\"mord mtight\"><span class=\"mord mathnormal mtight\">u</span><span class=\"mrel mtight\">∈</span><span class=\"mord mtight\"><span class=\"mord mathnormal mtight\" style=\"margin-right:0.10903em;\">U</span><span class=\"msupsub\"><span class=\"vlist-t vlist-t2\"><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:0.3281em;\"><sp